output:
Lighting a match and breathing gasoline
Firing the guns of emptiness
Roaming the days in invisibility
Lurking in constant oblivion
Watch the parade
Blame them of delusion
What is wrong with them is wrong with me too

Reckoning thoughts of misfortune tales
Run through the wires of fate
Sunburned faces on forgotten morning
Sitting side by side with emptiness
Watch the parade
Blame them of insanity
What is wrong with them is wrong with me too

Watch the parade
Blame them of delusion
What is wrong with them is wrong with me too
